Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:04.47,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我为了不让其毁坏而太过于珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:10.39,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}今天我也输入邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:16.26,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但又将其删除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:18.66,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}这样的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.83,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}将其打破的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:25.67,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}为我带来契机的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:29.65,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}用手心将其紧握
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:33.23,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}将现在改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:36.72,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}虽然也有苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:40.59,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使将碎片全部收集齐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:43.79,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也必须用自己的双手将其指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:46.49,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}极其珍视的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:49.84,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我害怕将其失去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:55.53,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但是我所希望的这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:58.81,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}都存在于此
